// and deployment environments that block common audio CDNs, so self-contained
// assets are the reliable choice here, same reasoning as the self-hosted
// MediaPipe WASM runtime). Each clip is short, low-sample-rate mono audio —
// intentionally lightweight, not high-fidelity.
